            p I am calling to oppose Trump's Executive Order abandoning the EPA Clean Power Plan. I am disgusted that Trump’s EPA cares more about the coal power industry than keeping our air clean, stopping global climate change, and moving our country past its reliance on fossil fuels. EPA should be protecting our environment instead of coal power plants! 

            p I want the senator to publicly call for the Trump administration and Scott Pruitt to stop this Executive Order and return to the Clean Power Plan, a sane and smart way to help our environment. 
            
